      • findSpeciesProb

        public static int findSpeciesProb(Species sp)

      • else loops through the entire ArrayList and pulls out the integer in the data[] at index 1. Because of arrayList the array must be cast to Object[]

Returns:

  • readExternalProbabilityLogic

    public void readExternalProbabilityLogic(java.io.ObjectInput in)
                                  throws java.io.IOException,
                                         java.lang.ClassNotFoundException
    Method to read in logic to calculate bison grazing probability. This includes fire history data, water distance data, land burned history data, fire historical weight, water distance weight, land burned weight if version is less than version 5 the data must be cast to ArrayList, if version is less than 3 weights must be gotten from integer data .
    Overrides:
    readExternalProbabilityLogic in class Process
    Throws:
    java.io.IOException

  • writeExternalProbabilityLogic

    public void writeExternalProbabilityLogic(java.io.ObjectOutput out)
                                   throws java.io.IOException
    Writes to an extrernal source the logic used to calculate bison grazing probability. This will be in order, fire history data, water distance data, land burned data, fire historical weight, water distance weight, land burned weight, default probability and species probability data.
